nodes.text: Zinethium was a rare and deadly material.

In 13 ABY, a team of thieves attacked the class-3 toxic weapons dump on Nyara to retrieve a chunk of zinethium. Several of them died in the attempt, but the surviving members escaped the planet under fire with the zinethium.
The leader of the team met with Nom Anor on the planet Adumar and turned over the chunk to him.
